      "text": "愛とこころも到着したそうよ\n「コメント録りは先に始めててちょうだい」――っと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai and Kokoro have arrived too‚ apparently.\n“Go ahead and start recording the comments first‚” she says.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3030.3344965,
          "startTime": 14.5970000823
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6700.001080900001,
          "startTime": 18.2666666667
