    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日はついに……あの番組の撮影ですね\n莉央さん、緊張してますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today’s finally the shoot for that program…\nRio-san‚ are you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.1423345566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "別に、そんなに身構えてはいないわよ\nむしろ、こんな番組観てくれる人いるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not really. I’m not that on edge about it.\nIf anything‚ I wonder if anyone will even watch a show like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8423356374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです。BIG4になって\nファンがますます増えたおかげで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course they will. Since becoming one of the BIG4‚\nyour fanbase has grown even more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2436269443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "新しいファンから「過去のリズノワを知りたい」って\n要望が沢山届いたんでしょ。何度も聞いたわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve received lots of requests from new fans saying\nthey want to learn about LizNoir’s past. I’ve heard it many times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8769613584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.9769587517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "私達の仕事は、ファンの声に応えることだし\nドキュメンタリーを撮るのは構わない。でも名前が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our job is to listen to our fans‚\nso I don’t mind filming a documentary. But the title…",
        "id": ""
      },
